{"tid":747256,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【佳寶淋液案】警拘13人　其中5漢持雙程證　料為遊客被招攬「兼職」","createTime":"2018-07-18T08:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T09:12:06.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ed17672e7f7a2db393dba04e8707044451451027","tid":747256,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180718/s00001/bc8cfc5bcb4f5fd8638d2b658018fa48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180718%2Fs00001%2Fbc8cfc5bcb4f5fd8638d2b658018fa48.jpg&h=ada48e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佳寶食品超級市場5間分店的豬肉檔上周先後遭人淋潑懷疑漂白水，導致3名職員受傷送院。警方今午押解一名26歲疑犯重返慈雲山分店重組案情。<br />\n<br />\n今天下午3時，警方西九反黑行動組押解該名26歲持內地雙程證疑犯到慈雲山毓華里1至23號的佳寶食品超級市場，重組案情。疑犯穿紅色人字拖，被鎖上手銬、纏上鐵鏈，向警員講述案發經過。其間警員在場拍攝。疑犯逗留約10分鐘後被帶走。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，至今拘捕13名中國籍男子，當中8人為持香港身分證的本地居民，另5人持雙程證來港，相信持雙程證的5人來港原本目的為旅遊，其間被人招攬做兼職工作，收取幾百至幾千元報酬，但5人不了解工作詳情，到作案前方獲告知地點及細節。<br />\n<br />\n警方又稱，數宗案件皆針對佳寶，初步調查後認為與商業貨物買賣糾紛有關，相信有關超市入貨時找到較便宜貨源，繼而調低原來入貨量，以至遭人襲擊，涉及的貨物金額不小。<br />\n<br />\n警方相信案中負責施襲的人至少5個，而大部分主腦已歸案，但不排除再有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n案發在本月11日，佳寶位於黃大仙、慈雲山、美孚、深水埗和油麻地的5間分店的豬肉檔，在兩小時內先後遭人淋潑懷疑漂白水。警方至今拘捕13人，他們涉嫌串謀刑事毀壞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180718/s00001/1531900839245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180718%2Fs00001%2F1531900839245&d=fGgTHmipv3bGgdzButwhimxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=74510356\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180718%2Fs00001%2F1531900839245&h=ea2b5053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180718/s00001/1531900839245</a>"},{"pid":"e8741d5175209d38b66543c414f5599fdfee350b","tid":747256,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:47:23.000Z","msg":"支那狗兼職淋漒水？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f713570af746ed2729023f7687f1c17675256151","tid":747256,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:56:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a12ffc3e37ad8aaaa54e37d63d5f5b16b1df0bc","tid":747256,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:58:08.000Z","msg":"留名睇鄰國人輕判，入哂本地人數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97acce886715edfd60de8ff21c98a2754988127b","tid":747256,"uid":23120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:01:47.000Z","msg":"新界仔搵人打？"},{"pid":"3e87859927ae2d228718830564f25b40a912f950","tid":747256,"uid":166663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"佳寶﹐千年雪藏肉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}